Ingredients/Biotin

Biotin

VitaminsEssential Capsules
Description

A B-vitamin (B7) essential for fatty acid synthesis, amino acid metabolism, and glucose metabolism. Important for healthy hair, skin, and nails.

Molecular Formula: C10H16N2O3S

Mechanism of Action

Cofactor for carboxylase enzymes involved in fatty acid synthesis, gluconeogenesis, and amino acid catabolism. Regulates gene expression via histone biotinylation

Blueprint Dosage

50mcg (167% DV)

MetabolismHair and nail healthSkin health
